      },
      "description": "HTTP and gRPC requests per second grouped by route and method. Excludes health check routes (ready, /grpc.health.v1.Health/Check) and self-scrape (metrics) which are high-volume noise. Push routes (loki_api_v1_push, otlp_v1_logs, /logproto.Pusher/Push) dominate under normal write load.",
