      "description": "Number of ACTIVE members per internal Loki ring (ingester, distributor, compactor, scheduler). In single-binary mode each ring should always show exactly 1 ACTIVE member. A drop to 0 on any ring means that component has left the ring — it will stop processing its workload until it rejoins.",
